\v 4 N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n me pam, n…ôp…®n iakam…ôfwaki tukumiaha, iakam…ôfwaki rer…®k rama…°ien  
\v 5 t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô fwe iak…®n…ôrer vi a mani irapw n…ô…°kiariien amasan muvehe meste pehe ipwet m…®ne sam…ôuvehi p…ôri r…ô…°…®taha me tukwe.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1Kor 1:8, Fil 2:13\x*N…ôn…ô iakukur…ôn amasan m…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®no stat ia noien amasan ia k…®miaha, in tram…ôkeikei mamo noien n…ôha mamev…ôn meste tro sampam ir…ô ia n…ôp…®n s…ô Iesu Kristo truvehe ir…ô.   
