\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Sam 2:11, 1Pit 1:17\x*N…ôrmama keikei me s…ôiou. N…ôp…®n iakamar…ô ihi k…®taha m k…®miaha, hiamo n…ôkwak ia n…ôp…®n me. N…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha iakamar…ô isipw…®n tukumiaha, k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mhousari mho n…ôkwak mamh…ôuv…ôn. Tih…ôhek…®r mh…ôt…ômn…®mw…®n mamho narimnari me n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehim…®ru k…®miaha tukwe.  
