\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Rom 15:16, 2Tim 4:6\x*Nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha r…ômwhen ia nari riti hiam…ôuvei pen m Kumwes…ôn kauvani ia t…ôkure n…®fat…ô. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô kousi …ôpune iou n…®tek raiu r…ômwhen ia waen k…ôt…ô…°i irapw ia n…ôri n…ôha, m…ôt…ô iou iakokeikei a mama…°ien k…®taha m k…®miaha.  
